 evolution, Cold War interregnum, and post-Mao renewal of Rockefeller philanthropy brings new clarity to the nature and tenacity of this ongoing bilateral relationship.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aHISTORY / Asia / China.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080477786540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804777865423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804777865/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles